rows.label: qst100408_msg0001
rows.name:
Flyers worked wonders! Customers
coming from far and wide to
hear song and eat food!

rows.label: qst100408_msg0002
rows.name:
Falala cook so much food that
skills improved dramatically!

rows.label: qst100408_msg0003
rows.name:
News of Falala's fame will definitely
reach ears of sonnypon Solala!

rows.label: qst100408_msg0004
rows.name:
But... Just reaching
sonnypon is not enough.

rows.label: qst100408_msg0005
rows.name:
Falala want sonnypon to come
back home... Want to see
his happy face again...

rows.label: qst100408_msg0006
rows.name:
Thank you. Maybe friends heard
some rumor of Solala on travels?

rows.label: qst100408_msg0007
rows.name:
Is that so... Maybe friends should
listen out for more rumors!

rows.label: qst100408_msg0008
rows.name:
Falala will also stop by the
informant to see if there any news!

rows.label: qst100408_msg0101
rows.name:
Must save money to buy
news from informant...

rows.label: qst100408_msg0102
rows.name:
Perhaps friends could ask
even more people for
information of Solala...?
